// frontend/src/components/Profile.js import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; export default function Profile({ user }) { const [stats, setStats] = useState({ totalEntries: 0, totalSpent: 0, totalLiters: 0, avgPrice: 0, joinDate: null }); useEffect(() => { // Calculate user stats const joinDate = new Date(user.createdAt || Date.now()); setStats(prev => ({ ...prev, joinDate: joinDate.toLocaleDateString('en-IN', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' }) })); }, [user]); return (
{user.name.charAt(0).toUpperCase()}

{user.name}

{user.email}

Member since
{stats.joinDate}
📊 Your Fuel Tracking Stats
{stats.totalEntries}
Total Entries
₹{stats.totalSpent.toFixed(0)}
Total Spent
{stats.totalLiters.toFixed(1)}L
Total Fuel
₹{stats.avgPrice.toFixed(2)}
Avg Price/L
🎯 Quick Actions
🏆 Achievements
🚗 First Entry 💯 10+ Entries 📅 Regular User
); }
